query:
INSERT INTO product_categories (productId, categoryId, isPrimary)
SELECT DISTINCT p.id, 13, 1
FROM products p
LEFT JOIN product_categories pc ON p.id = pc.productId
WHERE pc.productId IS NULL
AND (
  p.name LIKE '%Vial%' OR
  p.name LIKE '%vial%' OR
  p.name LIKE '%Cap%' OR
  p.name LIKE '%cap%' OR
  p.name LIKE '%Septa%' OR
  p.name LIKE '%septa%'
);
